<pre>String s = "A";</pre>
<p>Value of characters can be represented as hexadecimal value that run from \u0000 TO \uFFFF . For Example ,\u2122 is a trademark symbol  for &#x2122; and 
\u03C0 is greek letter &#x03C0;</p>
<p>There are other types of escape sequences also for special characters . We can use them in quoted literal characters as </p>
